snippet.title: BLOODKILL - Gameplay Trailer 2
snippet.description:
BRUTAL First Person Shooter focused on action, gore and blood-pumping metal music.

Kill hordes of evil monsters, find secret items, master bunny hopping, and tear enemies apart with powerful guns!

Play a game inspired by classic shooters like DOOM, Quake, Painkiller. Enjoy non-stop action and gameplay without interruptions.
